{"tid":1346712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要分上環定元朗，根本係同一黨人做嘅嘢，請大家聚焦清楚","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:52:32.000Z","uid":13754,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e719463c078c51d5dd3cbca758d4594c7b903ccb","tid":1346712,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"係同一黨人分成兩批同時喺上環同元朗向平民施襲<br />\n<br />\n而唔係話重視某個地方，呢個社會嘅唔安寧都係呢一黨人造成<br />\n<br />\n唔好再分上環定元朗，我哋要將呢班人噚日所做嘅嘢集合埋一齊，畀所有人都知道"},{"pid":"e92a846ed0d8e7e9d943edc05fe2ae4170465138","tid":1346712,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"呢一黨人噚日可以喺上環元朗做嘢，他日都可以喺柴灣粉嶺做嘢，唔好再拘泥喺邊度發生呢啲事住，佢哋做過咩毛我哋一定要逐樣計"},{"pid":"ad0800ea1d2873bf9b3fbcab33488312be937c06","tid":1346712,"uid":176112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ce6de8004638743a8b07860ee6086af0f67461d8","tid":1346712,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad0800ea1d2873bf9b3fbcab33488312be937c06","tid":1346712,"uid":176112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"c3c37122912092d4bae15481418b031e114a85a9","tid":1346712,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6de8004638743a8b07860ee6086af0f67461d8","tid":1346712,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad0800ea1d2873bf9b3fbcab33488312be937c06","tid":1346712,"uid":176112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T